  "comment": "96x3W high power and portable outdoor wireless battery wash light\nSmart Book is a wireless battery wash light, performing high output in a super-slim foldable housing. Smart Book, being IP rated, is an ideal tool for outdoor events to light up landscapes and buildings, all with a magnetic optical system (+50° included) to focus the light. Smart Book comes with a quick magnetic recharge flight case and control through wireless DMX.\n",
